ing aggregated. Investigator UI role: read of case state and OpenSearch case index scoped by case-assignment claim; write of investigator-decision events to [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mcase-actions[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m bus only. Audit indexer role: read on flag bus; write to OpenSearch flag-audit index only. Documentation-assist Lambda role: read on case state for the specific case being processed; Bedrock invoke; Comprehend Medical detect; write of assessment back to case state for the specific case only. Outcome-capture Lambda role: write to [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mcase-outcomes[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m S3 bucket only; write of label rows; no broader case-state write."[K
