[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    223[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;143;161;179m###[38;2;192;197;206m [38;2;143;161;179mArchitecture Expert Review[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    224[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    225[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;143;161;179m####[38;2;192;197;206m [38;2;143;161;179mWhat's Done Well[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    226[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    227[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe four-detector architecture (rules, statistical, graph, ML) feeding a unified evidence aggregator that builds case bundles is the architecturally correct factoring for FWA detection. The decision to run different layers at different cadences (rules and eligibility-integrity in the streaming path; statistical baselining as weekly per-provider batch; graph analytics as daily; supervised re-ranking as quarterly retraining) reflects realistic operational tempos.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    228[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The data-foundation-takes-60%-of-the-first-year framing is the most candid program-design framing in any cookbook recipe and is operationally accurate. Most FWA detection projects underdeliver because they invert this ratio.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    229[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The case-management-as-the-product framing ("the detection pipeline produces scored candidates. The investigators produce cases, and cases produce recoveries") is the right reframe and the recipe is explicit about it. The Honest Take's "build case management before the third detector" lesson is the corollary teaching most first-time builders miss.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    230[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The Graph-Is-The-Secret-Sauce subsection is the strongest single-architectural-contribution in any chapter-3 recipe. The framing that the graph differentiates mature programs from immature ones, combined with the explicit "everything else can be done with flat tabular analytics and you'll catch a fraction of the money," is the kind of design-constraint-up-front teaching that the cookbook is built on.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    231[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The community-detection-as-Louvain choice is operationally accurate; Louvain (and its faster variant Leiden) is the standard graph-community-detection algorithm in production fraud analytics. Naming it explicitly (rather than "graph clustering") is the right teaching specificity.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    232[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The cost estimate is unusually defensible: "$5,000-16,000/month" infrastructure cost framed against "5x to 15x" SIU recovery ROI from mature programs. The HTML-comment TODO acknowledging that SIU ROI benchmarks need verification before publication is the right discipline. The "infrastructure cost is a small fraction of investigator staffing cost and a smaller fraction of recoveries" framing is operationally accurate and is exactly the framing leadership conversations need.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    233[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The implementation-time tiers (6-10 months Basic, 15-24 months Production-ready, 18-36 additional months for variations) are realistic and resist optimism bias. The Basic tier explicitly excludes graph analytics, GNN, supervised ML re-ranker, and LLM-assisted documentation; this is the right scoping.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    234[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m Variations and Extensions covers the right adjacent patterns at substantive depth: pharmacy-focused, home health and hospice specialization, DME and prosthetics, behavioral health, real-time pre-payment integrity (with the correct note that pre-payment integration produces higher ROI but substantially higher operational complexity), member-facing fraud, LLM-native investigation assistance, cross-payer intelligence sharing via Clean Rooms, explainable case generation, federated learning, provider-facing transparency. The cross-payer sharing extension correctly references the Healthcare Fraud Prevention Partnership as the entry point.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    235[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The Why This Isn't Production-Ready section's fourteen substantive bullets cover the right operational disciplines. The investigator-workflow-as-the-product bullet, the entity-resolution-is-a-full-project bullet, the legal-and-privileged-architecture bullet, the regulatory-referral-infrastructure bullet, and the change-management-for-rule-releases bullet are each tied to real production concerns. The fairness-bias-equity bullet is unusually substantive for a non-clinical-decision-support recipe.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    236[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    237[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;143;161;179m####[38;2;192;197;206m [38;2;143;161;179mFinding A1: Outcome-Event Idempotency Not Modeled at the Evidence-Aggregator Lambda[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    238[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    239[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mSeverity:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m MEDIUM[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    240[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mExpert:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Architecture[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    241[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mLocation:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Step 7 [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mon_flag_event[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m (consumed via EventBridge from [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mfwa-flags[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m bus); Architecture Diagram ([38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mX[Amazon EventBridge\nfwa-flags] --> Y[AWS Lambda\nevidence-aggregator][38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m).[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    242[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The architecture is event-driven from the four detector layers (rules, statistical, graph, supervised re-ranker) to the evidence-aggregator Lambda via EventBridge. EventBridge guarantees at-least-once delivery; Lambda asynchronous invocation also retries on failure. If EventBridge redelivers a flag event (the Lambda's first attempt timed out, the detector's PutEvents call retried after a transient error, or any of the failure modes documented in the recurring trigger-idempotency findings across Recipes 2.4-2.10 and 3.1-3.5), the evidence-aggregator runs twice on the same flag. Each run:[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    243[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    244[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m1[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mAppends the flag to [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mcase.flags[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m ([38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mcase.flags.append({ flag: flag, detected_at: NOW(), detector: flag.detector_source })[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m). The append produces duplicate flag entries on the case; the case's combined-dollar-impact computation ([38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mcompute_combined_dollar_impact(case.flags)[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m) double-counts; the priority score ([38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mcompute_priority_score(case.evidence_bundle, program_priorities())[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m) is derived from the doubled dollar impact and is therefore distorted; cases that should rank below the case-review threshold rise above it because of doubled flags; the investigator queue depth is artificially inflated.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    245[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    246[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m2[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mRe-fetches the subgraph and peer comparison[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m ([38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mfetch_subgraph(target, hops = 3, weighted_by = "paid_amount")[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m, [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mbuild_peer_comparison(target, flag)[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m). These are expensive operations against Neptune and the feature store; redelivery doubles the cost without producing additional value.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    247[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    248[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m3[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mRe-publishes the [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mCaseReady.triage[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;235;203;139m event[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m if the doubled priority score crosses the review threshold. The triage queue now has duplicate triage events for the same case, the analyst tooling displays the case twice, and the analyst-workflow-tracking metrics are corrupted.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    249[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    250[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mSame recurring trigger-idempotency pattern as Recipes 2.4-2.10, 3.1, 3.2, 3.3, 3.4, 3.5 (twelfth consecutive recipe). The fix template is the same.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    251[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    252[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mFor Recipe 3.6 specifically the consequence is calibrated to the regulatory-referral pathway: a doubled priority score on a case that is on the edge of the regulatory-referral threshold can flip the case from "investigation only" to "regulatory referral" or vice versa. For Medicare Advantage organizations under 42 CFR 422.504(h), the timing and accuracy of the referral is itself a compliance posture. A case that should not have been referred and was referred wastes regulator resources; a case that should have been referred and was not produces FCA exposure for the payer.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    253[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mFix:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Two-part fix:[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    254[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m1[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m Derive a deterministic event key from the flag identifier ([38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mflag.flag_id[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m plus [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mflag.detector_source[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m), and use it as a write-once guard in DynamoDB:[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    255[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m     [38;2;191;97;106m```[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    256[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m     event_key = flag.flag_id + "|" + flag.detector_source[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    257[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m     try:[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    258[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m         DynamoDB.PutItem([K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    259[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m             table = "processed-flag-events",[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    260[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m             item  = { event_key: event_key, processed_at: NOW() },[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    261[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m             condition = "attribute_not_exists(event_key)"[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    262[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m         )[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    263[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m     except ConditionalCheckFailedException:[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    264[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m         emit_metric("flag_event_duplicate_dropped", 1)[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    265[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m         RETURN[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    266[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m   ```[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    267[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m     [38;2;191;97;106mThe processed-flag-events table can have a TTL of 90 days. This prevents the case-flag append, the subgraph fetch, and the triage-event publish from running twice for the same flag.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    268[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m2[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m Add a "Trigger idempotency" bullet to "Why This Isn't Production-Ready" tying the discipline to the recurring chapter pattern.[K
