[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    277[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m No Dead Letter Queue or [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mOnFailure[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m destination is configured for any Lambda in the pipeline. The recipe's own "Why This Isn't Production-Ready" section names "Disaster recovery and continuity" as a core production concern with the framing "a quarter without FWA detection is a quarter of undetected schemes." But the per-event poison-message recovery discipline is at a different abstraction level than that paragraph addresses.[K
