[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    290[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mFix:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Add four SQS DLQs to the Architecture Diagram: [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mstream-normalizer-dlq[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m, [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mrules-engine-dlq[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m, [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mevidence-aggregator-dlq[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m, and [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140moutcome-capture-dlq[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m. Add a Prerequisites note: "Configure each Lambda's [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mOnFailure[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m destination to a dedicated SQS DLQ. CloudWatch alarms on DLQ depth alert the on-call SIU-engineering team; for the stream-normalizer-dlq specifically, alarm threshold should be 1 because a single dropped claim is a claim that escaped scoring. Replay events from DLQ after fixing the root cause; for events older than the regulatory-referral compliance window, escalate to compliance-team review rather than auto-replay because the timing-of-detection is itself part of the compliance posture under 42 CFR 422.504(h) and 42 CFR 438.608." Add a "DLQ and replay" bullet to "Why This Isn't Production-Ready" that ties the discipline to the existing disaster-recovery paragraph.[K
