[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    454[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The recipe correctly specifies CloudTrail (with data events on every PHI-bearing store and case data store) for control-plane and data-plane API audit. It does not explicitly require VPC Flow Logs, which capture network-level access patterns (source/destination IPs, ports, protocols, accept/reject) and are part of the standard HIPAA audit posture and the SIU regulatory-investigation posture.[K
